<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 08:10:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列通过敬献花圈和大屠杀纪念馆纪念大屠杀纪念日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-marks-holocaust-remembrance-day-with-wreath-laying-yad-vashem-ceremony/0000018f-4c7d-d414-a5bf-ff7fa1560000</link><description>随着警报声使国家陷入停顿，全国各地将举行仪式。周日晚上，内塔尼亚胡在大屠杀纪念馆举行的一次活动中表示，“即使我们必须孤立无援，我们也将继续与人类的邪恶作斗争”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:24:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-marks-holocaust-remembrance-day-with-wreath-laying-yad-vashem-ceremony/0000018f-4c7d-d414-a5bf-ff7fa1560000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谈判濒临崩溃，内塔尼亚胡摆出了拒绝主义的姿态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/with-hamas-talks-on-the-verge-of-collapse-netanyahu-puts-up-a-rejectionist-front/0000018f-4a51-d6c3-afdf-4f530dfb0000</link><description>中央情报局局长被派往中东，努力挽救人质协议，而内塔尼亚胡被认为是主要障碍。美国压力的大小将决定他是否答应拜登总统的要求</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/with-hamas-talks-on-the-verge-of-collapse-netanyahu-puts-up-a-rejectionist-front/0000018f-4a51-d6c3-afdf-4f530dfb0000</guid></item><item><title>关闭半岛电视台是以色列搬起石头砸自己的脚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/by-shutting-down-al-jazeera-israel-is-shooting-itself-in-the-foot/0000018f-4a76-dcda-abcf-6a77785b0000</link><description>通过关闭卡塔尔新闻网络，以色列加入了一个由阿拉伯国家组成的杰出俱乐部，该俱乐部已经停止了半岛电视台的运营。此举应该令以色列媒体感到担忧，因为以色列媒体被禁止在加沙地带内部独立进行广播</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/by-shutting-down-al-jazeera-israel-is-shooting-itself-in-the-foot/0000018f-4a76-dcda-abcf-6a77785b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列开始从拉法撤离；国防部长称哈马斯别无选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-live/idf-three-soldiers-killed-near-gaza-border/0000018f-4ba4-dcda-abcf-6ba7979b0006</link><description>以色列国防军开始从拉法东郊撤离约 10 万巴勒斯坦人 ■ 哈马斯对加沙过境点的迫击炮袭击造成 3 名士兵死亡、9 人受伤 ■ 哈马斯重申人质交易的出发点是结束战争 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列不会屈服于哈马斯的要求结束战争 ■ 中央情报局局长前往中东，官员称加沙停火谈判濒临“崩溃”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-live/idf-three-soldiers-killed-near-gaza-border/0000018f-4ba4-dcda-abcf-6ba7979b0006</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部和北部夜间发生枪击事件，两名男子丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/two-men-killed-in-overnight-shootings-in-central-and-northern-israel/0000018f-4bfe-dcda-abcf-6bff97570000</link><description>警方怀疑至少其中一起事件与有组织犯罪有关</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 21:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/two-men-killed-in-overnight-shootings-in-central-and-northern-israel/0000018f-4bfe-dcda-abcf-6bff97570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府抛弃了其公民。但反对派几乎没有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-05/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-has-abandoned-its-citizens-but-the-opposition-offers-little-hope/0000018f-49cc-d6c3-afdf-4ddf0a700000</link><description>每一位宁愿与本格维尔和内塔尼亚胡共处一室，也不愿在街头与那些呼喊他们的人在一起的以色列民选官员都选择了错误的一边</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 20:58:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-05/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-has-abandoned-its-citizens-but-the-opposition-offers-little-hope/0000018f-49cc-d6c3-afdf-4ddf0a700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在加沙迫击炮弹袭击中丧生的三名士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-mortar-barrage-from-gaza/0000018f-4a7b-d91a-a5af-ebffec900000</link><description>塔尔·沙维特、鲁本·马克·莫迪凯·阿苏林、伊多·泰斯塔这三名士兵正在看守军队在拉法行动之前部署的装备。哈马斯袭击中另有九名士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 20:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-mortar-barrage-from-gaza/0000018f-4a7b-d91a-a5af-ebffec900000</guid></item><item><title>据报道加沙停火谈判陷入“困境”，中央情报局局长前往以色列挽救协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-talks-reportedly-in-tough-spot-cia-chief-heads-to-israel-to-rescue-deal/0000018f-4a4b-d17f-adcf-fbebfac90000</link><description>参与谈判的消息人士称，尽管哈马斯做出了积极回应，但以色列拒绝派遣代表团前往埃及讨论该协议。哈马斯重申立场 要求以色列全面撤出加沙</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 20:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-talks-reportedly-in-tough-spot-cia-chief-heads-to-israel-to-rescue-deal/0000018f-4a4b-d17f-adcf-fbebfac90000</guid></item><item><title>尽管气氛充满敌意，以色列的铁杆粉丝仍希望在马尔默为欧洲歌唱大赛加油</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/die-hard-israeli-fans-hope-to-cheer-on-eurovision-in-malmo-despite-hostile-vibes/0000018f-48e4-d414-a5bf-fbf7bcfe0000</link><description>决定前往瑞典马尔默的球迷表示，他们并不担心计划中的反以色列示威活动，但在赛场外“不想引起注意”或让其他人知道他们是以色列人</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:41:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/die-hard-israeli-fans-hope-to-cheer-on-eurovision-in-malmo-despite-hostile-vibes/0000018f-48e4-d414-a5bf-fbf7bcfe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列选择在10月7日点燃独立日火炬 行动因威胁而取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chosen-to-light-independence-day-torch-cancels-due-to-threats/0000018f-491d-d17f-adcf-f9ffcc3f0000</link><description>以色列南部莫沙夫亚泰德的居民纳斯林·优素福 (Nasreen Yousef) 审问了 10 月 7 日渗透到她所在地区的恐怖分子，但社区反应小组的成员表示，她夸大了自己在挫败袭击中的作用。她说她取消是因为她和她的家人受到威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:19:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chosen-to-light-independence-day-torch-cancels-due-to-threats/0000018f-491d-d17f-adcf-f9ffcc3f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 212 天：中央情报局局长前往多哈与卡塔尔总理举行紧急会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-212-cia-chief-travels-to-doha-for-emergency-meeting-with-qatari-pm/0000018f-49ab-d414-a5bf-fbbfede50001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡表示“以色列不能接受”哈马斯结束加沙战争的要求 ■ 以色列国防部长：哈马斯显示出不打算达成协议的迹象，这意味着拉法行动将在“不久的将来”启动 ■ 中央情报局局长伯恩斯出差前往多哈与卡塔尔总理举行紧急会议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府一致投票决定关闭以色列半岛电视台 ■ 战争进入 212 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 16:59:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-212-cia-chief-travels-to-doha-for-emergency-meeting-with-qatari-pm/0000018f-49ab-d414-a5bf-fbbfede50001</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和辛瓦尔都需要获胜，因此加沙战争将继续下去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/both-netanyahu-and-sinwar-need-to-win-so-the-gaza-war-will-carry-on/0000018f-4978-d6c3-afdf-4d7bac470000</link><description>大多数以色列人和加沙人都明白，他们失去了太多，在这场战争中没有任何“胜利”的概念。但只要他们的命运掌握在两个坚持成为胜利者的人手中，不惜一切代价，这场战争就会继续下去</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 16:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/both-netanyahu-and-sinwar-need-to-win-so-the-gaza-war-will-carry-on/0000018f-4978-d6c3-afdf-4d7bac470000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列北部发射重型火箭弹；大楼被撞，两人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-heavy-rocket-barrages-at-northern-israel-building-hit-two-wounded/0000018f-496b-d6c3-afdf-4d7bba610000</link><description>以色列军方称，从黎巴嫩向上加利利发射了约 40 枚火箭弹。作为回应，以色列袭击了黎巴嫩真主党目标；黎巴嫩新闻媒体报道四名平民死亡、两人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 16:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-heavy-rocket-barrages-at-northern-israel-building-hit-two-wounded/0000018f-496b-d6c3-afdf-4d7bba610000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列不能接受哈马斯结束加沙战争的要求；国防部长：拉法攻势迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-cannot-accept-hamas-demand-to-end-war-gallant-rafah-offensive-imminent/0000018f-491b-d91a-a5af-e9ffa33f0000</link><description>据报道加沙谈判取得进展，国防部长加兰特在加沙内部表示，以色列认识到“哈马斯不打算遵守任何协议的令人震惊的迹象”；哈马斯领导人哈尼亚重申该组织的出发点是停止战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 15:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-cannot-accept-hamas-demand-to-end-war-gallant-rafah-offensive-imminent/0000018f-491b-d91a-a5af-e9ffa33f0000</guid></item><item><title>《周六夜现场》回避学生抗议，选择与家长轻松取笑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/snl-sidesteps-student-protests-and-opts-for-lighthearted-fun-at-their-parents/0000018f-48e1-d17f-adcf-f9e318340000</link><description>该短剧以脱口秀圆桌会议为特色，主持人询问家长对抗议活动的感受</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 15:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/snl-sidesteps-student-protests-and-opts-for-lighthearted-fun-at-their-parents/0000018f-48e1-d17f-adcf-f9e318340000</guid></item><item><title>他们小时候逃离了纳粹。现在他们因为真主党而无法回家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-escaped-the-nazis-as-children-they-are-still-not-home-because-of-hamas/0000018f-484f-d6c3-afdf-4d5f3b520000</link><description>过去七个月里，数十名从黎巴嫩边境附近什洛米撤离的以色列人，包括约 20 名大屠杀幸存者，一直住在耶路撒冷的一家酒店里</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 13:18:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-escaped-the-nazis-as-children-they-are-still-not-home-because-of-hamas/0000018f-484f-d6c3-afdf-4d5f3b520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列纪念大屠杀之际，“生者游行”在欧洲开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/march-of-the-living-set-to-begin-in-europe-as-israel-commemorates-the-holocaust/0000018f-484a-d6c3-afdf-4d5b5b700000</link><description>从奥斯威辛到比克瑙的无声游行以及穿越布达佩斯的游行，“生者游行”标志着二战结束时几个月内超过 55 万匈牙利犹太人被杀害。在以色列，10 月 7 日之后的大屠杀纪念日将呈现不同的面貌</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 12:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/march-of-the-living-set-to-begin-in-europe-as-israel-commemorates-the-holocaust/0000018f-484a-d6c3-afdf-4d5b5b700000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡希望哈马斯拒绝停火提议。如果没有，他就转向破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hoped-hamas-would-reject-israels-offer-when-it-didnt-he-turned-to-sabotage/0000018f-4817-d414-a5bf-fb37db290000</link><description>以色列刑事被告总理更专注于拯救无能的极右翼政府，而不是拯救被困在加沙七个月的人质，他正在竭尽全力破坏以色列将人质带回家的最后也是最好的机会</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 11:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hoped-hamas-would-reject-israels-offer-when-it-didnt-he-turned-to-sabotage/0000018f-4817-d414-a5bf-fb37db290000</guid></item><item><title>照片：耶路撒冷另一种火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-photos-a-different-kind-of-fire-in-jerusalem/0000018f-4814-d516-afbf-fed6e4cc0000</link><description>“圣火”仪式已经举行了一千多年。这就是上周在耶路撒冷庆祝的方式</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 11:14:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-photos-a-different-kind-of-fire-in-jerusalem/0000018f-4814-d516-afbf-fed6e4cc0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡内阁一致投票决定关闭以色列半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/israeli-government-votes-unanimously-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018f-4841-d91a-a5af-e9f5c8de0000</link><description>以色列通讯部长称赞这一决定“结束了该网络运转良好的煽动机器”；以色列警方突袭该频道耶路撒冷办事处并没收设备；半岛电视台猛烈抨击这一决定，称其为“诽谤性和欺骗性的举动”</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 11:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/israeli-government-votes-unanimously-to-shut-down-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018f-4841-d91a-a5af-e9f5c8de0000</guid></item></channel></rss>